<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.1455509>
    dc:description "FIGURES 3–5. Dicerura penttineni, male, holotype. 3: Genitalia, ventral. 4: Ninth tergite, dorsal. 5: Tegmen and ejaculatory apodeme, ventral. Scales 0.05 mm. Arrows refer to characters described in the diagnosis." ;
